cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.DS 

This paper deals with constructing and evaluating preference queries in a database, which falls under the category of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also discusses query modification and preference relations, which are topics related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions algebraic laws for incremental evaluation, which is a topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) and data structures (cs.DS).
